{"tid":1071441,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有咩PS4手掣適合玩格鬥game？","createTime":"2019-03-21T10:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T12:07:51.000Z","uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e7f3dbdc5f2f4e93457f81b66742b23a609d74","tid":1071441,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好同我講JOYSTICK</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nJOYSTICK咁撚大件又咁撚貴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hori.jp/products/p4/fps_plus_bk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhori.jp%2Fproducts%2Fp4%2Ffps_plus_bk%2F&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3IdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=98a23205\" target=\"_blank\">https://hori.jp/products/p4/fps_plus_bk/</a><br />\n呢隻ok嘛？十字掣，又有touch pad(有d格鬥game按start係都要人按右touch pad，係都唔set比人按option作為start咁撚閪)"},{"pid":"6ee6cb618ea5ea6e8b740b49a5eabee7eef0ab1f","tid":1071441,"uid":4767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hori.jp/image/2017/11/3c1eea3729b281b92cb6d4e6212cbed8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhori.jp%2Fimage%2F2017%2F11%2F3c1eea3729b281b92cb6d4e6212cbed8.jpg&h=0f009260&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b00ffe8d0f1e1c0a4dc8473c58d82fbe963d2a95","tid":1071441,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee6cb618ea5ea6e8b740b49a5eabee7eef0ab1f","tid":1071441,"uid":4767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hori.jp/image/2017/11/3c1eea3729b281b92cb6d4e6212cbed8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhori.jp%2Fimage%2F2017%2F11%2F3c1eea3729b281b92cb6d4e6212cbed8.jpg&h=0f009260&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"呢隻冇touch pad，有d 格game按唔到start"},{"pid":"c8215ae46f9b6fb6a7383b3df02d0c3261cc1feb","tid":1071441,"uid":78568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"原廠制已經夠玩<br />\n街霸五好多比賽冠軍都係原廠制<br />\nE.G. NuckleDu Punk MenaRD <br />\n日本仔後生嘅都有 John Takeuchi <br />\n如果龍珠呢啲操作相對簡單嘅 手制反而係主流<br />\n街霸有啲角色可能手制比較難操作<br />\n好似上面巴打po 嘅<br />\njoystick咁上下各三粒制嗰種手制可能會比較輕鬆<br />\n(利申未用過)<br />\n你呢隻嗰八粒制分佈都同原廠冇咩分別<br />\n同埋唔比你用Option制當start係好事<br />\n你打比賽hi到pause咗當你輸 1 round<br />\n而家Joystick設計多數可以俾你打比賽嗰陣鎖咗個PS同Option制<br />\n所以有啲game先會冇呢個設定"},{"pid":"d93b8a28aa3d324a87aaa91ed450e01c4d19aca6","tid":1071441,"uid":62458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBFkdSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBFkdSf.png&h=4a007d51&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}